titles.title: A concurrent resolution directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to correct the enrollment of H.R. 6063.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Mr. Lampson asked unanimous consent to take from the Speaker's table and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary:
10/2/2008--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Makes corrections to the enrollment of H.R. 6063 (National Aeronautics and Space Administration Authorization Act of 2008).
